---
// Process Section Component
---

<section class="process section animate-on-scroll" id="process">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-tag">⚡ Our Process</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">From Struggling to Dominating in 90 Days</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Our proven 4-step system is helping Sydney businesses transform from invisible to industry leaders. Here's exactly how we do it.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="process-timeline">
      <div class="process-step animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="process-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-search-plus"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="process-content">
          <h3>Deep-Dive Analysis</h3>
          <p>We audit your current digital presence, analyze your competitors, and identify the exact opportunities that will drive the biggest impact for your business. No guesswork—just data-driven insights.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <div class="process-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-chess"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="process-content">
          <h3>Strategic Planning</h3>
          <p>Based on our analysis, we create a customized growth strategy that targets your ideal customers, maximizes your budget, and delivers measurable results within 90 days.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="process-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="process-content">
          <h3>Rapid Implementation</h3>
          <p>We execute your strategy with precision and speed. From website optimization to ad campaigns, everything is implemented according to our proven framework for maximum impact.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="step-number">4</div>
        <div class="process-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="process-content">
          <h3>Optimize & Scale</h3>
          <p>We continuously monitor, test, and optimize your campaigns to ensure peak performance. As results improve, we scale successful strategies to drive even greater growth.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>